Fab course. I love the hand-on experience. Much better than learning this in college! 
The instructor is great at teaching concepts and applying them with examples. I had to practice as advised by the Instructor, but it greatly helped me pin down the concepts. I am much more confident now than before. Definitely recommend this course for student struggling with core Java/Hibernate concepts. Thanks.
